description:
FULL English coverage of the live Europa League Group A match between Spanish giants Valencia and the rising Premier League force, Swansea City.

Swansea's Europa League adventure begins with a trip to Spain to face La Liga giants Valencia.

It's a tasty opener for Michael Laudrup, who got his side into Europe thanks to their Capital One Cup win last season, and will be looking forward to testing himself against one of the continent's bigger clubs.

Los Che include former Spurs striker Helder Postiga within their ranks, who will be looking to show what he can do after a disastrous spell in England.

Watch Valencia v Swansea live on ITV4 and ITV.com on Thursday 19 September from 5.30pm.
